About this item

EMERGENCY TUBELESS TYRE PUNCTURE KIT: Flat Tire Puncher Repair Kit is designed to provide you quick solution for fixing a tubeless tyre during your road trip. It is equipped with all tools that are ideal to quickly fix a puncture in your tire.

PREMIUM UPGRADED 5 STRINGS: This set comes included with 5 BROWN strings that offers superior safety seal. These repair strip plugs offer a much stronger and long-lasting solution than BLACK strings found in other kits. Every aspect this Tire Plug Kit is engineered to be strong so it will last for years to come.

ERGONOMICALLY DESIGNED T-HANDLE TOOLS: The offered set includes rubber- grip durable T-handles probe and reamer that becomes the right anti-slip tool for the job, making it easy to repair punctures in any tubeless tire in minutes. Set includes easy to use tools for quick-fix.

VERSATILE FLAT TIRE REPAIR KIT: An all-in-one puncture repair kit to fix tubeless tires of your Cars, Motorcycles, ATVs, Tractors, Lawn Mowers, RV, Dirt Bikes, Trailers, Jeeps, Trucks and Spare Tire Repair Kit. Travel with peace of mind and enjoy the driving with our tire repair little kit.

PRO GRADE TOOLS INCLUDED: You will need plier for every repair. Our flat tire repair kit includes a solid pair of T-handle probe and reamer. A BIG UPGRADE to the skinny cheap tools found in other tire plug repair kits along with a durable case to keep it all organized and secure.
